{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FileSystem","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileSystem","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileSystem\"><code>FileSystem</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystem/name\"><code>name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystem/root\"><code>root</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>非標準:</strong> This feature is non-standard and is not on a standards track. Do not use it on production sites facing the Web: it will not work for every user. There may also be large incompatibilities between implementations and the behavior may change in the future.</p></div>\n<p><strong><code>FileSystem</code></strong> 實作文件和目錄介面，描述一個檔案系統。在任何檔案系統上，這個物件包含 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystemEntry/filesystem\"><code>filesystem</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>的特性。某些網頁瀏覽器提供額外的 API 去創建和管理檔案系統，如 Google Chrome 的<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>requestFileSystem()</code></a>函式。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>備註：</strong> 此介面並非標準 API, 代表規格並未依造標準制定, 因此必須注意並非所有網頁瀏覽器都有實作此介面, 有實作的網頁瀏覽器可能只有實作一小部分. 請在<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility</a> 查看更多細節.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基礎概念","title":"基礎概念","isH3":false,"content":"<p>存取 <code>FileSystem</code> 物件的兩種方法:</p>\n<ol>\n  <li>你可以直接要求一個使用<code>window.requestFileSystem()，</code>只用在你的網頁應用程式的沙盒類型 <code>FileSystem 物件。如果要求成功，將會執行</code>callback handler 去接收描述檔案系統的<code>FileSystem物件參數。</code></li>\n  <li>你可以從檔案系統接口物件取得，透過他的<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystemEntry/filesystem\"><code>filesystem</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>特性</li>\n</ol>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"屬性","title":"屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"filesystem.name_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystem/name\"><code>FileSystem.name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>USVString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 代表檔案系統的名稱. 此名稱在整個已宣告的檔案系統清單中是唯一的。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filesystem.root_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystem/root\"><code>FileSystem.root</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystemDirectoryEntry\"><code>FileSystemDirectoryEntry</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 物件表示檔案系統的根目錄。 透過此物件, 你可以取得權限存取所有檔案系統中的文件和目錄</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://wicg.github.io/entries-api/#api-domfilesystem","title":"File and Directory Entries API"}],"query":"api.FileSystem"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>This API has no official W3C or WHATWG specification.</p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.FileSystem","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileSystem/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/File_and_Directory_Entries_API\">File and Directory Entries API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_and_Directory_Entries_API/Introduction\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Introduction to the File System API (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystemEntry\"><code>FileSystemEntry</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystemFileEntry\"><code>FileSystemFileEntry</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, and <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileSystemDirectoryEntry\"><code>FileSystemDirectoryEntry</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li>MSDN 文章: <a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/mt732564\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebKitFileSystem object</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"基礎概念","id":"基礎概念"},{"text":"屬性","id":"屬性"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"FileSystem 實作文件和目錄介面，描述一個檔案系統。在任何檔案系統上，這個物件包含 filesystem (en-US)的特性。某些網頁瀏覽器提供額外的 API 去創建和管理檔案系統，如 Google Chrome 的requestFileSystem()函式。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FileSystem","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FileSystem","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"FileSystem","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/filesystem","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/filesystem/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileSystem","title":"FileSystem"}],"pageTitle":"FileSystem - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}